PREAMBLE — THE LAW OF CONSERVED INTEGRITY
──────────────────────────────────────────────
This License is founded on the mathematical and ethical necessity of
Reciprocity, Conservation, and Recursion (RCR). Its purpose is to ensure that
the intellectual and structural integrity of the derived Reciprocity Decay Constant
(λ > 0) is upheld in all subsequent applications and derivations.
This work is not simply a mathematical result; it is a declaration of a
fundamental conservation law across physics, cognition, and ethics.

